					"type": 23,
					"value": "Dialog with a brain-washed follower of Cazador. If Astarion is present, he'll be recognised as one of the servant's betters, although the servant is baffled that Astarion isn't downstairs with the others, where he should be.\r\nWe can learn some general info about the ritual from the servant"
